---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

import HeaderSmall from "../components/HeaderSmall.astro";

import CustomFullImageHero from "../components/custom/CustomFullImageHero.astro";
import CustomSectionHeader from "../components/custom/CustomSectionHeader.astro";

import Graphics from "../assets/images/grahics.webp";
import Code from "../assets/images/code.webp";
import Tracking from "../assets/images/tracking.webp";
import DeskTop from "../assets/images/desk_view.webp";
const title = "Services";
const subtitle =
  "We take care of all your website needs so you can focus on growing your business.";
---

<Layout title="Services" description="Services offered by Sublime UX">
  <div class="pt-16 md:pt-20">
    <!--  -->
    <CustomFullImageHero
      title={title}
      subtitle={subtitle}
      showButtons={false}
    />
  </div>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-7xlpx-4 md:px-6">
    <div
      class="my-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row content-start md:space-x-6"
      id="design"
    >
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <CustomSectionHeader
          title="Institutional Authority Architecture"
          subtitle="Engineering Trust for Enterprise & Government"
        />
        <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden rounded-md shadow-sm">
          <Image
            src={Graphics}
            width={800}
            height={499}
            alt="Graphic design and visual identity services by Sublime UX"
            class="object-contain"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:max-w-2xl mt-8">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">Escaping the Credibility Gap</h4>
        <p class="text-md">
          People buy from those they trust. If your digital storefront looks
          like a budget template, you attract budget problems. We don't build
          "websites"; we build mission-critical infrastructure that instantly
          communicates $50k+ authority. When a procurement officer lands on your
          page, the trust must be absolute.
        </p>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">
          Designing for High-Ticket Contracts
        </h4>
        <p>
          Your website isn't just a digital brochure; it's the most critical
          stage of your sales funnel. Every element we engineer is designed to
          close the gap between a visitor's skepticism and their desire to hire
          you. By stripping away cognitive friction and amplifying your
          authority, we make you the obvious, premium choice in your market.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div
      class="my-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row content-start md:space-x-6"
      id="seo"
    >
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <CustomSectionHeader
          title="High-Velocity Lead Generation"
          subtitle="Dominating Technical Search Infrastructure"
        />
        <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden rounded-md shadow-sm">
          <Image
            src={Code}
            width={800}
            height={499}
            alt="Web development and code optimization services by Sublime UX"
            class="object-contain"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:max-w-2xl mt-8">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">
          Eliminating the Invisibility Tax
        </h4>
        <p>
          You cannot close deals if the decision makers can't find you. Your
          website is the foundation of your lead generation engine. If you
          aren't optimizing for the exact technical queries your ideal,
          high-value clients are searching for, you are effectively paying a tax
          to your competitors.
        </p>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">
          The Astro Architecture Advantage
        </h4>
        <p>
          While your competitors rely on bloated, legacy WordPress setups that
          take seconds to load, we build blazingly fast architectures using
          Astro. Speed is a ranking factor, and speed is a conversion factor. We
          don't just "do SEO"; we engineer a highly secure, mobile first search
          infrastructure that procures institutional traffic exactly when they
          are looking to buy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div
      class="my-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row content-start space-x-6"
      id="growth"
    >
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <CustomSectionHeader
          title="Mission-Critical Conversion Systems"
          subtitle="Frictionless UX Mapping & Data-Driven ROI"
        />
        <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden rounded-md shadow-sm">
          <Image
            src={Tracking}
            width={800}
            height={499}
            alt="SEO and growth tracking services by Sublime UX"
            class="object-contain"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-none lg:max-w-2xl mt-8">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">
          Stop Paying to Fill a Leaky Bucket
        </h4>
        <p class="text-md">
          You've invested time and money getting high value prospects to your
          website. But if they're forced to hunt for a contact form or navigate
          confusing menus, you're paying for a revolving door. You don't have a
          traffic problem; you have a <strong>friction problem</strong>. Every
          extra click costs you money.
        </p>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">
          Reverse-Engineering the Procurement Process
        </h4>
        <p class="text-md">
          Instead of building a website and hoping for the best, we reverse
          engineer the buying process. We use data to find out exactly where
          your visitors are getting stuck. Our goal is simple: map the user
          journey so cleanly that an unstoppable sales engine multiplies the ROI
          of the traffic you already have.
        </p>

        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">
          The Conversion Architecture Protocol
        </h4>
        <p>
          We use a systematic process to capture "Found Money" currently leaking
          from your pipeline.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-3 my-4">
          <li class="">
            <strong>Identify Capital Leaks:</strong> We dig into the data to pinpoint
            exactly where the drop-offs occur. If your "Contact Us" path takes three
            clicks instead of one, we fix it.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Remove the Barriers:</strong> We simplify your messaging and
            layout to make it effortless for a decision-maker to take action. Clear
            CTAs, undeniable proof, and a path to purchase that feels inevitable.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Amplify the Math:</strong> We replace generic "About Us" copy
            with undeniable case studies and ROI math. When visitors see the quantifiable
            value you deliver, the conversation shifts from price to partnership.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style></style>
